## Execution Flow

```
main()
  ↓
rclcpp::init()                    ROS2 initialized
  ↓
std::make_shared<MyNode>()        →  MyNode() constructor runs:
                                       - Node("cpp_test") sets name
                                       - prints "Hello world"
                                       - registers timer (does NOT fire yet)
  ↓
rclcpp::spin(node)                BLOCKS — processes callbacks
                                  every 1 second → timerCallback() fires
                                  ↓
                                  "Hello 0", "Hello 1", "Hello 2", ...
                                  ↓
Ctrl+C                            spin returns
  ↓
rclcpp::shutdown()                clean exit
```

